data.description: ASK ABOUT 2/1 RATE BUY DOWN. This 2122 SF haven boasts not only a spacious interior but also a backyard oasis that will make every day feel like a vacation! Generously-sized POOL and Covered Patio. The main floor features a versatile bedroom/den, providing an ideal space for a home office or guest suite. The open layout leads to the heart of the home, kitchen boasts Granite Counter Tops-Walk In Pantry. Breathtaking views of both the Sunrise Mountains and the iconic Strat. The second-floor loft, complete with a balcony, provides the perfect vantage point to savor these vistas. Home has paid off water softener system as well as security system. Pool Pump recently replaced cost $2000. This home also has solar panels with low monthly payments! Tucked away at the end of a tranquil cul-de-sac, this home has it all. Whether you're seeking a quiet evening under the stars or an exciting day exploring the Strip, 1170 Fogg St provides the perfect base to experience the best of Las Vegas living.
